* Custom graph scheme
* Based on Stata's official s2color scheme with minor visual modifications

*! version 1.0.0   2026-04-23

#include s2color

color background white
color major_grid "200 200 200"

color p1 "128 195 66"
color p2 navy

anglestyle vertical_tick horizontal

clockdir legend_position 4
numstyle legend_cols 1
linestyle legend none
margin legend "5 0 0 0"
